<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.222690>
    dc:description "FIGURES 35 – 45. Sternoppia fissurata sp. nov., adult: 35 — prodorsum, lateral view (gnathosoma, epimeral setae and legs not shown); 36 — notogaster, posterior view; 37 — rostrum, dorso-anterior view; 38 — rostral seta; 39 — lamellar seta; 40 — interlamellar seta; 41 — sensillus; 42 — exobothridial seta; 43 — notogastral seta lp; 44 — genital plate, left; 45 — anal plate, left. Scale bars (35, 36) 50 μm, (37 – 45) 10 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/222690/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

